Package io.github.jansky.ezroute

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bus
    Bus represent the various buses in Singapore
    BusRoute
    BusRoute contains a Bus and the origin and destination BusStop, including the number of stops between the origin and destination, inclusive of both stops.
    BusRouteActivity
    BusRouteActivity is the activity for each individual bus route.
    BusRoutesAdapter
    BusRoutesAdapter takes BusRouteActivities and will generate the list display structure for the BusRouteListActivity.
    BusRoutesListActivity
    BusRoutesListActivity is the activity that contains and generates all the BusRoutes viewed on screen.
    BusStop
    BusStop is the representation of a bus stop in Singapore.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    MapsActivity
    The MapsActivity is the functionality of the Google Maps view that is on screen.
    Singleton
    The Singleton class is a singleton that handles requests for the server calculations.
    UnitTests
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
